  <section class="home-section">
    <div class="title-body-content">
      <h2>Welcome to Buoy Viewer</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="body-content">
      <div class="text">
        <p>Welcome to Buoy Viewer, a web aplication able to represent and analyse scientific buoys information distributed around the world.</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <p>This service offered by Buoy Viewer is divided in two functionalities: 'Map' and 'Analyse'.</p>
          <li><h4>Map:</h4></li>
            <p>
              The 'Map' service allows the user to visualize and interact with the information showed in the map via points that, when clicked, will pop-up a bit of the information of the buoy. 
              This service will also allow the users to download data in different formats.
            </p>
          <li><h4>Analyse:</h4></li>
              <p>
                The 'Analyse' service allows to get a deeper analysis of the buoys belonging to a specific cruise. 
                This service only can be accessed if the user is logged in.
              </p>
          <li><h4>About Us: </h4></li>
            <p>
              In the 'About us' section you will find information about the creators of Buoy Viewer, 
              and in the 'Contact us' you will be able to contact via e-mail for providing feedback.
            </p>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="image"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
